file.name: info.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3

info:
  title: OpenAPIArt Test API
  description: |-
    Demonstrates the features of the OpenAPIArt package
  version: 0.0.1
  contact:
    x-info: |-
      Any feedback such as bugs/enhancements/questions regarding OpenApiArt is 
      welcomed by using the contact url.      
    url: https://github.com/open-traffic-generator/openapiart/issues

servers: 
  - url: https://{hostname}:{port}/{basePath}
    variables:
      hostname:
        default: 0.0.0.0
      port:
        default: "8080"
      basePath:
        default: api

paths: {}
